Yingli ‘Well Prepared’ for Solar Industry Downturn, CFO Li Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-06-20T04:34:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-20/yingli-well-prepared-for-solar-industry-downturn-cfo-li-says.html
Yingli Green Energy Holding Co. is
“well prepared” for a downturn in the solar industry, Chief
Financial Officer Li Zongwei spoke to reporters in Baoding city
in central  China ’s Hebei province.  “It is really quite healthy for the industry,” Li said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
